Author: AlexanderAltoCar
Title: ğŸŒŸ[ALTOCAR]ğŸŒŸ - REVOLUTION IN TAXI
Body: ALTOCAR NEWS(03/20/2018)  We apologize for the delay in the answer! For 4 months we worked on the search for venture investors. The results of the negotiations were definite, as successful, but after a long time, investors refused to invest in the project, due to the general fall of the market. Unfortunately, we did not get cooperation with these investors.  It is difficult to develop the project without investment, but, according to the project, the work continues and we do not intend to give up!  What was done in 4 months?  - 3 investors were found, but after extending the time they refused to invest - Let's remind, burning of superfluous tokens have made. The total number of tokens that remains is 1,586,500. - Tokens are sold only on the DEX exchange (while the rest did not work together) - In the service we launched the "Delivery of Cargo" for legal entities - Made internal improvements on the platform - Increased average travel check - Improved mobile apps - Finished in 2017 with a result of 19 million rubles. revenue ($ 322,000) - Currently we work only in Kazan, Russia  Plan 2018  February-March - Developed a plan to enter the market of individuals with a minimum budget March-August - Entering the market of individuals August-October - After full-fledged entry into the market of individuals, we intend to introduce a loyalty system based on ALTOCAR tokens for customers and drivers. December - Implementing a loyalty system for a franchise. Listing on the stock exchange Yobit, Bittrex  2019-2020 Expansion of business - advancement on cities at the expense of own means, sale of the franchise in Russia and on the world. Listing on Binance, Kucoin, HitBTC.  In parallel, we continue to search for investors for the project. As soon as something is known about this, we will immediately inform our communities, but only when the deal is concluded.  Thank you for your patience, the work on the project is ongoing and we do not intend to stop!

At the moment, negotiations with a large fund and several large private investors on investing a significant amount in the development of AltoCar are quite positive. Author: AlexanderAltoCar
Title: ğŸŒŸ[ALTOCAR]ğŸŒŸ - REVOLUTION IN TAXI
Body: DEAR PARTICIPANTS OF ALTOCAR ICO!  ICO is completed, we thank everyone who participated and supported us! While the ICO process, 2,146,346 ALTOCAR tokens were sold for $ 2,500,000 (as of November 10, 2017). Under the terms of the ICO, the softcap was $ 3,600,000. We remind you that under the terms of the ICO, the invested funds must be returned to the ICO participants. Also we remind that presale was successful in July-August with $ 300 000 equivalent in ALTOCAR tokens.  The reasons why the ICO did not take place in full power (in our opinion):  Most investors (by the way, members of the bounty campaign too) prefer to invest in tokens based on ETHEREUM, and not on WAVES We were in three forks (Bitcoin CASH, Bitcoin GOLD, Segwit2x). Many investors, including those with whom we regularly met, kept funds for this reason. Also, due to forks, bitcoin showed great growth in a short time. During this period, a large number of ICO came out and we simply disappeared in this mass Perhaps we did not fully communicate the essence of our project to the community In some moments, we were brought up by partners in advertising Many investors informed us that they are interested in purchasing tokens after the ICO from the exchanges  On ICO: Due to the fact that the soft-cap wasn't achieved, the funds will be returned to the ICO participants within 14 days (until 24.11.2017). We believe that this will be correct in relation to all participants.  On PRESALE: Since the presale passed successfully - the tokens will be transferred to the participants of the presale in full. Also, the presale participants will be subject to the conditions that were specified during the presale.   WE WORK FURTHER, MEET - PLAN "B"!  WE REMIND YOU THAT WE ARE ALREADY WORKING COMPANY, A COMPANY THAT ALREADY MAKES INCOME, SO WE CONTINUE OUR WORK AND IMPLEMENTING TOKENS TO THE SERVICE, NOT LOOKING AT ANYTHING!  In the ICO process, we also negotiated with classical venture investors who invest in the development of companies through fiat money. At the moment, negotiations with a large fund and several large private investors on investing a significant amount in the development of AltoCar are quite positive. The funds will be used to scale up business in the big cities of Russia. The franchise will also be available for purchase.  Tokens will be introduced into the service economy and placed on stock exchanges, as it was planned in our White Paper. First of all, we will start using ALTOCAR tokens in Kazan, where we have been working successfully for more than 2 years. Tokens will be used by customers, drivers, partners and other stakeholders. The road map will be finalized.  During the presale, airdrop and bounty campaign, 1 110 550 ALTOCAR tokens were sold.  Under the terms of the ICO, the tokens will be distributed as follows (in proportion):  Participants of the PRESALE, bounty, airdrop (70%) - 1 110 550 ALTOCAR For introduction into the economy of service and founders (30%) - 475 950 ALTOCAR. Total remains on the market - 1,586,500 ALTOCAR.  The remaining 30,413,500 tokens will be burned. The address of the wallet to which the tokens to be burned will be sent - will be reported publicly.  All participants of the presale, airdrop, bounty campaigns will get ALTOCAR tokens in full, and within the specified period (within 7 days after the completion of the ICO), according to their shares.  If there are ICO investors who wish to leave ALTOCAR tokens and do not receive a refund - write to us from their email (which is the login on dashboard.altocar-ico.com). You will get ALTOCAR tokens.  The ALTOCAR tokens will be available today at the DEX exchange. Within two weeks, the tokens will be placed on the Tidex exchange. Also, we are negotiating with HitBTC.  ATTENTION TO THE PARTICIPANTS OF THE BOUNTY!  As the work on the service continues, we will have additional offers for participation. It will be necessary to distribute our news, we are ready to give tokens for this.  Our assumptions about the cost of the ALTOCAR token for the next 6 months:  In the first month / second month after the distribution of the tokens, we expect a drop in value, which is due to the fact that the tokens will be sold by the bounty campaign participants. Further, after the introduction of ALTOCAR tokens into the service economy, demand for it is expected to rise among the members of the AltoCar service itself.  From our side, we will make efforts to develop the ALTOCAR service and token. Stay in groups in telegram and social networks, we will share news on the project.  THANKS FOR YOUR ATTENTION, EVERYTHING IS OK, THE WORK CONTINUES, ALTOCAR WILL GO FURTHER! ğŸ˜‰  Team AltoCar, CEO Alexander Bobylev.

Author: neeviktor
Title: ğŸŒŸ[ALTOCAR]ğŸŒŸ - REVOLUTION IN TAXI
Body: Increase softcap Hello!  Having carried out additional financial analysis, we came to the conclusion that they made a mistake:  Running the service with an insufficient number of community members, holders of ALTOCAR tokens, we run the risk of not achieving the results indicated in White Paper, so we decided to increase the soft cap to $ 3.6 million. This soft cap will give us the opportunity to fully Start a service in 3 cities with a population higher 1 million people (at a rate of 1.2 million per city) and achieve all the necessary indicators.  Having launched 3 cities within 5 months after the end ICO we will get a huge demand for ALTOCAR tokens from ~ 100,000 people. Cities that we plan to fully launch in the first place: Kazan, Rostov-on-Don and Krasnodar (Russia). In the city data, our partner in drivers is already present and it is ready to be launched. We also intend to distribute the franchise in parallel.  ATTENTION! 1. If the soft store is not reached, the invested funds will be returned to the participants of the Crowdsale, in the currency in which the investment was made. 2. Tokens not realized at the time of crowdsale will be burned.  At the moment involved: More than $ 180,000 from more than 300 participants! Do not miss the chance to get tokens with an excellent bonus!  Tokens can be purchased for Bitcoin, Ethereum, Waves, Litecoin, Ethereum Classic, Dash, ZCash.  Current Bonus 25%.  Join now!   ALTOCAR - The first global blockchain franchise personalized taxi After the completion of the ICO, it is planned to launch the franchise of the service and its promotion around the world. The franchise will be sold to any country, to any city in the world. Packing the franchise will take 2 months after the ICO, in parallel, pre-orders for it will be accepted.  The franchise can be purchased only for ALTOCAR tokens. Payment of royalty franchisees will be made only in ALTOCAR tokens. This will erase the borders between countries - it will not be necessary to conduct procedures with banks, currency transactions, etc. Pianos from the Franchisee will be paid almost instantly.  Franchisees will provide services to customers (transportation), pay drivers on a dual model - in ALTOCAR tokens and in a fiat.  Also, customers and service drivers will receive bonuses in ALTOCAR tokens after performing certain actions (reaching KPI, viewing advertising on trips, etc.).  Thanks to all the above, the service will receive explosive growth, the turnover of tokens will grow many times. As a result, a huge community of people using ALTOCAR tokens in everyday life will be formed.

The use of tokens in the service ecosystem will begin no later than 4 months after the completion of the ICO. How will the token participate in the economy of the service and its ecosystem?  â€¢ Customers will be able to travel for tokens â€¢ When traveling for tokens, customers will be able to get a discount for the trip (up to 30%) â€¢ Customers will be able to view advertising during the trip (optional) earning additional tokens, which they can then use for travel â€¢ The company will encourage drivers tokens for excellent performance â€¢ Drivers will be able to save a certain percentage of daily earnings for the purchase of tokens through the driver application â€¢ Drivers who own tokens will receive priorities for larger orders â€¢ Through our gateway, drivers will be able to exchange tokens for petrol, car wash services, car repairs, tire shops, food and much more The implementation of tokens into the Service economy  Bonuses for ALTOCAR tokens holders: â€¢ 500 tokens owner gets 10 free trips per month â€¢ 750 tokens owner gets 15 free trips per month â€¢ 1000 or more tokens owner gets 20 free trips per month Limitation for each trip: travelling distance is no longer than 10 km, in time â€“ no more than 20 minutes.  Note: The trips that were not used in the past month are burned.

All conditions for using tokens in the economy remain  Within two years many countries and cities are going to be implemented our service.  The AltoCar franchise can only buy tokens on exchanges, with which they will not only have to pay the franchise, but also purchase tokens for the domestic economy. Author: neeviktor
Title: ğŸŒŸ[ALTOCAR]ğŸŒŸ - REVOLUTION IN TAXI
Body: With the help of raised funds on the ICO, we plan to implement the service in 13 million-population cities of Russia in 18 months. The implementation of the service in Moscow and St. Petersburg is planned on the second stage of the service expansion plan. Why can we launch 13 millionaire cities in 18 months? â€¢ We have worked out an effective scheme for quickly attracting customers through trusted channels. â€¢ There is a well-developed scheme for attracting and motivating drivers â€¢ We have a general partner who operates in 11 cities of Russia and provides us and other services with drivers. With this partner we have been cooperating for 2 years in Kazan. He is ready to work with us in other cities as well. â€¢ We have developed AltoCar platform, which allows you to set up work in another city in within 1 day (only the platform, then you need marketing, etc.).  How will the token participate in the economy of the service and its ecosystem? â€¢ Customers will be able to travel for tokens â€¢ When traveling for tokens, customers will be able to get a discount for the trip (up to 30%) â€¢ Customers will be able to view advertising during the trip (optional) earning additional tokens, which they can then use for travel â€¢ The company will encourage drivers tokens for excellent performance â€¢ Drivers will be able to save a certain percentage of daily earnings for the purchase of tokens through the driver application â€¢ Drivers who own tokens will receive priorities for larger orders â€¢ Through our gateway, drivers will be able to exchange tokens for petrol, car wash services, car repairs, tire shops, food and much more The implementation of tokens into the Service economy  Bonuses for ALTOCAR tokens holders: â€¢ 500 tokens owner gets 10 free trips per month â€¢ 750 tokens owner gets 15 free trips per month â€¢ 1000 or more tokens owner gets 20 free trips per month   We will constantly stimulate demand for tokens in our economy, this will give rise to tokens.

Body: AltoCar service connects passengers and drivers. The main feature is the ability to add drivers to the 'Favorites', and to use only their services in the future.  The service operates in the B2C and B2B segments.  For two years of operating in the taxi market of Kazan (Russia), AltoCar company has launched and is running: service of drivers by subscription, service for corporate clients, service for individuals.  AltoCar service carried out more than 90 thousand trips, the total length of trips has been estimated up to 1.35 million kilometers  At the moment the Service is an acting business:  8000 employees of organizations and individuals 100+ organizations of Kazan: banks, well-known retail companies, construction and oil companies and many others. 5000+ drivers in the service database  Total revenue of $ 500,000 (28 million rubles)  With the help of raised funds on the ICO, we plan to implement the service in 13 million-population cities of Russia in 18 months.

Title: ğŸŒŸ[ALTOCAR]ğŸŒŸ - REVOLUTION IN TAXI
Body: Yes, the system is already operating in the city of Kazan, Russia.  For two years of operating on taxi market of Kazan (Russia), AltoCar company has launched and running: service of drivers by subscription, service for corporate clients, service for individuals. AltoCar service carried out more than 90 thousand trips, the total length of trips has estimated up to 1.35 million kilometers (data for one city for July 2017).  Now we are launching ICO to scale the system for million-population cities of Russia, and after that go global.
